&lt;p&gt;Using one default image for all posts:&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>How to Create SEO-Optimized Blog Posts with Hugo Paper's New-Post Script</title><link>https://hugopaper.github.io/post/create-seo-optimized-posts-hugo-paper-new-post-script/</link><pubDate>Fri, 15 Nov 2024 10:00:00 +0800</pubDate><author>Hugo Paper Team</author><guid>https://hugopaper.github.io/post/create-seo-optimized-posts-hugo-paper-new-post-script/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;Creating blog posts with proper SEO optimization can be time-consuming. Hugo Paper&amp;rsquo;s &lt;code&gt;new-post&lt;/code&gt; script automates this process, helping you create well-structured, SEO-friendly posts in seconds.&lt;/p&gt;
